demand of firms, or

01:01:06.840 --> 01:01:09.070
the expenses of the state,

01:01:09.080 --> 01:01:11.310
or the expenses of foreigners change?

01:01:12.310 --> 01:01:14.770
What factors are these components dependent on?

01:01:16.360 --> 01:01:18.080
That is what we will talk about now.

