of all consumers, or national

01:01:40.060 --> 01:01:41.430
income.

01:01:42.720 --> 01:01:45.200
From accumulated wealth, from

01:01:45.210 --> 01:01:46.100
the size of consumer

01:01:46.110 --> 01:01:48.140
debt, consumer expectations,

01:01:48.150 --> 01:01:50.080
taxes, transfers,

01:01:50.180 --> 01:01:52.440
interest rate.

01:01:54.160 --> 01:01:55.820
Well, let's talk about some

01:01:55.830 --> 01:01:58.720
of these factors a little.

01:02:00.800 --> 01:02:01.480
Well look at.

