You will put more money off on a

01:04:19.390 --> 01:04:20.180
black day.

01:04:20.960 --> 01:04:22.600
In other words, you will

01:04:22.610 --> 01:04:25.300
save most of your income.

01:04:25.680 --> 01:04:27.500
Your expenses will decrease.

01:04:27.950 --> 01:04:30.110
The curve of hell will then

01:04:30.120 --> 01:04:32.190
move to the left.

01:04:32.310 --> 01:04:33.370
If everyone thinks so.

01:04:33.630 --> 01:04:36.530
All consumers think that there

01:04:36.650 --> 01:04:38.470
are tough times ahead.

