By the way, these dependencies

01:10:43.510 --> 01:10:45.720
are often used by the government

01:10:45.960 --> 01:10:48.280
to conduct economic policy.

01:10:48.760 --> 01:10:51.040
Well, imagine the country's economy is

01:10:51.050 --> 01:10:55.860
experiencing a decline or stagnation.

01:10:56.120 --> 01:10:57.780
This was relatively recently,

01:10:57.790 --> 01:10:59.540
for example, in Japan.

01:11:00.680 --> 01:11:03.360
Economic growth has fallen to almost

01:11:03.370 --> 01:11:04.280
zero.

