The same with households.

01:12:08.760 --> 01:12:10.780
Even with low interest rates,

01:12:10.790 --> 01:12:13.980
they didn't have to spend much.

01:12:14.220 --> 01:12:16.580
Because their personal expectations

01:12:16.590 --> 01:12:18.160
of future income changes

01:12:18.170 --> 01:12:20.520
were unfavorable.

