The year 2003 was a pessimistic year.

02:25:27.100 --> 02:25:29.120
Look what happened.

02:25:29.460 --> 02:25:31.160
GDP has increased.

02:25:32.820 --> 02:25:35.620
Economists predicted that growth

02:25:35.630 --> 02:25:37.860
would stop or be minimal, and

02:25:38.460 --> 02:25:41.440
GDP in 2003 instead grew

02:25:41.450 --> 02:25:44.500
by 7.3%.

02:25:46.120 --> 02:25:47.190
What contributes?

02:25:48.390 --> 02:25:49.910
Please look at the third line

02:25:49.920 --> 02:25:53.430
of investment in capital.

02:25:55.240 --> 02:26:00.490
What happened to the investments in 2003?

02:26:02.980 --> 02:26:07.920
There was an investment boom.

02:26:08.040 --> 02:26:10.560
Increased investment costs

02:26:10.570 --> 02:26:11.920
of companies.

02:26:13.610 --> 02:26:17.470
But investments in the macroeconomy

02:26:17.480 --> 02:26:19.070
play a dual role.

02:26:21.830 --> 02:26:26.270
On the one hand, investment is a

02:26:26.280 --> 02:26:29.890
component of aggregate demand.

02:26:30.090 --> 02:26:32.350
When companies make investments,

02:26:32.360 --> 02:26:34.250
it means they order new equipment,

02:26:34.260 --> 02:26:36.330
for example, from machinery

02:26:36.370 --> 02:26:38.150
manufacturers.

02:26:41.300 --> 02:26:42.860
Investment is part of

02:26:42.870 --> 02:26:44.680
the total demand.

02:26:44.760 --> 02:26:47.000
When the equipment is purchased

02:26:49.180 --> 02:26:52.890
and installed, what happens as a result?

02:26:53.410 --> 02:26:56.230
The production capacity of the companies

02:26:56.240 --> 02:26:57.770
is increasing.

02:27:00.220 --> 02:27:01.840
But if the production capacity of firms

02:27:01.850 --> 02:27:04.880
grows, the potential GDP, that

02:27:04.890 --> 02:27:06.640
is, the opportunities of firms,

02:27:06.650 --> 02:27:08.100
increases.

02:27:11.230 --> 02:27:14.710
So, on the one hand, investments contribute,

02:27:14.720 --> 02:27:17.830
are a component of the aggregate

02:27:17.840 --> 02:27:19.510
demand.

02:27:19.710 --> 02:27:20.810
Growth in investment is an increase

02:27:20.820 --> 02:27:21.930
in overall demand.

02:27:22.090 --> 02:27:24.010
But on the other hand, the

02:27:24.020 --> 02:27:26.690
growth of investments means that firms

02:27:26.700 --> 02:27:28.930
have increased physical capital,

02:27:29.650 --> 02:27:30.970
more means of production.

02:27:31.510 --> 02:27:34.050
This means that the potential

02:27:34.060 --> 02:27:36.170
GDP will increase.

02:27:36.730 --> 02:27:39.630
This is the ideal situation.

02:27:39.990 --> 02:27:41.970
Please look at the schedule.

02:27:47.270 --> 02:27:49.490
We go back to the same schedule.

02:27:50.010 --> 02:27:52.290
You see, the overall demand

02:27:52.300 --> 02:27:53.930
continues to grow.

02:27:54.150 --> 02:27:56.090
The curve of hell has already moved to

02:27:56.100 --> 02:27:57.850
the position AD3.

02:27:59.760 --> 02:28:03.120
But by increasing investment, when

02:28:03.130 --> 02:28:05.240
equipment is installed, the potential

02:28:05.250 --> 02:28:08.500
GDP grows.

02:28:11.490 --> 02:28:15.810
Consequently, not only is the combined

02:28:15.820 --> 02:28:17.570
demand curve shifting to the

02:28:17.870 --> 02:28:20.530
right, but the long-term combined

02:28:20.540 --> 02:28:22.950
supply curve is shifting to the right.

02:28:23.010 --> 02:28:23.510
also also.

02:28:25.070 --> 02:28:26.890
This is an ideal situation.

02:28:27.050 --> 02:28:28.870
A kind of eternal engine.

02:28:29.990 --> 02:28:32.630
On the one hand, demand is growing,

02:28:32.640 --> 02:28:35.490
but the constant opportunities for

02:28:35.500 --> 02:28:37.130
its satisfaction, i.e. the total

02:28:37.140 --> 02:28:39.110
supply, are growing.

02:28:40.050 --> 02:28:41.990
Simultaneous demand of the total demand

02:28:42.000 --> 02:28:43.950
and the possibility of its

02:28:43.960 --> 02:28:44.890
satisfaction, i.e. the

02:28:44.900 --> 02:28:47.270
total supply, contributes

02:28:47.810 --> 02:28:52.550
to the constant growth of GDP.

02:28:54.310 --> 02:28:56.010
And now, please look at the situation

02:28:56.020 --> 02:28:59.370
of the fourth, fifth,

02:28:59.390 --> 02:29:00.000
sixth.

