So, ladies and gentlemen, let's start

02:44:06.610 --> 02:44:08.400
our seventh topic.

02:44:08.780 --> 02:44:11.760
Fiscal fiscal policy.

02:44:12.320 --> 02:44:14.000
Please look at the main issues of

02:44:14.010 --> 02:44:16.700
the topic.

02:44:16.920 --> 02:44:19.400
The first is the budget system of

02:44:19.410 --> 02:44:20.820
the Russian Federation,

02:44:21.260 --> 02:44:24.280
the state budget and its importance.

02:44:26.550 --> 02:44:28.490
The definition is very simple.

02:44:28.770 --> 02:44:31.030
Budget is a form of education

02:44:31.040 --> 02:44:33.330
and spending of funds to ensure

02:44:33.340 --> 02:44:35.510
the functions of state

02:44:35.520 --> 02:44:38.370
authorities and local self-government.

02:44:38.380 --> 02:44:42.730
The Russian budgetary system consists

02:44:42.740 --> 02:44:45.550
of three levels.

02:44:46.010 --> 02:44:48.090
The first level is the federal

02:44:48.100 --> 02:44:50.650
budget and the budgets of state non-

02:44:50.660 --> 02:44:52.110
budgetary funds.

02:44:52.910 --> 02:44:55.950
The second level is the budgets of the constituent

02:44:55.960 --> 02:44:58.930
entities of the Russian Federation and the

02:44:58.940 --> 02:45:02.070
budgets of territorial extra-budgetary funds.

02:45:02.550 --> 02:45:04.970
The third level is local budgets.

02:45:04.980 --> 02:45:08.630
All of these budgets together constitute

02:45:08.640 --> 02:45:10.970
the consolidated budget of

02:45:10.980 --> 02:45:13.070
the Russian Federation.

02:45:14.970 --> 02:45:17.590
In terms of how large the expenses

02:45:17.600 --> 02:45:19.770
of the consolidated

02:45:19.780 --> 02:45:22.830
budget can be said about the

02:45:22.840 --> 02:45:24.910
degree of state intervention

02:45:24.920 --> 02:45:26.650
in the economy.

02:45:28.050 --> 02:45:29.910
Consolidated budget

02:45:29.920 --> 02:45:31.490
spending is approximately

02:45:31.500 --> 02:45:37.490
27.5% of GDP.

02:45:37.730 --> 02:45:39.910
Compared to economically developed

02:45:39.920 --> 02:45:43.010
countries, this is a rather

02:45:43.020 --> 02:45:46.050
moderate figure.

02:45:46.530 --> 02:45:49.570
However, for a country, which is

02:45:49.580 --> 02:45:51.630
not yet very rich, this figure is

02:45:51.640 --> 02:45:54.290
considered to be quite large.

02:45:54.510 --> 02:45:57.090
What would be good would be to reduce

02:45:57.100 --> 02:46:00.350
the share of the state in the economy a little.

02:46:07.020 --> 02:46:10.180
The leading link in the budget

02:46:10.190 --> 02:46:12.160
system is the state or

02:46:12.170 --> 02:46:13.480
federal budget.

02:46:14.240 --> 02:46:16.320
This is the basic plan for the formation

02:46:16.330 --> 02:46:18.420
and use of the centralized monetary

02:46:18.430 --> 02:46:20.040
fund of the state.

02:46:21.600 --> 02:46:23.760
The federal budget, like any other,

02:46:23.770 --> 02:46:26.780
consists of the income and expenditure

02:46:26.790 --> 02:46:28.620
parts.

02:46:29.100 --> 02:46:31.780
The income part of the state

02:46:31.790 --> 02:46:34.420
budget is formed by taxes

02:46:34.430 --> 02:46:37.240
and non-tax revenues.

02:46:37.720 --> 02:46:40.040
The federal budget is charged

02:46:40.050 --> 02:46:42.740
basic taxes, such as VAT, excise

02:46:42.980 --> 02:46:46.120
duties, customs duties, mineral

02:46:46.130 --> 02:46:48.540
mining tax and others.

02:46:51.780 --> 02:46:53.280
The income part of the

02:46:53.290 --> 02:46:57.380
state budget does not include

02:46:57.390 --> 02:47:01.460
funds from the realization

02:47:01.470 --> 02:47:03.060
of state property, as well

02:47:04.650 --> 02:47:08.340
as loans on domestic

02:47:08.350 --> 02:47:10.540
and foreign markets.

02:47:12.540 --> 02:47:13.940
This is the income part.

02:47:15.080 --> 02:47:17.080
On the other hand,

02:47:17.090 --> 02:47:18.380
the state budget is formed,

02:47:18.390 --> 02:47:21.000
the main most important

02:47:21.010 --> 02:47:23.440
expenses related to priority

02:47:23.680 --> 02:47:26.780
investment programs,

02:47:26.790 --> 02:47:28.940
support for the most important

02:47:29.380 --> 02:47:32.100
sectors of the economy,

02:47:32.110 --> 02:47:34.740
social and cultural

02:47:34.750 --> 02:47:37.820
development, defense, law

02:47:37.830 --> 02:47:40.640
enforcement, education,

02:47:41.480 --> 02:47:44.300
healthcare and so on.

02:47:44.660 --> 02:47:47.620
In addition, the expenditure part

02:47:47.630 --> 02:47:50.980
of the budget includes payments

02:47:50.990 --> 02:47:53.560
of interest on state loans.

02:47:53.860 --> 02:47:55.920
The payment of the main amount,

02:47:55.930 --> 02:47:59.460
debt, in the expenditure part

02:47:59.470 --> 02:48:02.420
of the budget is not included.

02:48:03.080 --> 02:48:05.560
These payments are made at the

02:48:05.570 --> 02:48:08.260
expense of new loans or

02:48:08.270 --> 02:48:09.640
a surplus of the state

02:48:09.650 --> 02:48:10.900
budget, if any.

02:48:14.540 --> 02:48:17.640
The budget consists

02:48:17.650 --> 02:48:20.960
of two main

02:48:20.970 --> 02:48:24.780
parts.

02:48:24.840 --> 02:48:28.200
On the one hand, it is interest

02:48:28.210 --> 02:48:31.240
costs, that is, it is the cost

02:48:31.250 --> 02:48:32.500
of paying interest on

