So the conclusion.

02:55:34.140 --> 02:55:36.420
Money must be like water

02:55:36.430 --> 02:55:39.420
in nature, just as much as

02:55:39.430 --> 02:55:42.180
the economic soil can

02:55:42.190 --> 02:55:46.520
