a normal result, if that money

02:57:24.870 --> 02:57:26.800
is spent normally,

02:57:26.810 --> 02:57:29.860
it will be spent effectively.

02:57:30.800 --> 02:57:32.300
If, I repeat, they are not used effectively,

02:57:32.310 --> 02:57:33.960
they will either simply go to the

02:57:33.970 --> 02:57:36.200
sand, or they will turn the

02:57:36.210 --> 02:57:38.300
economic soil into mud, and we

02:57:38.310 --> 02:57:41.040
will only get a price increase.

