03:17:49.010 --> 03:17:51.090
Why a minus sign?

03:17:51.330 --> 03:17:55.410
Because if taxes rise, it will have

03:17:55.420 --> 03:17:57.590
a bad impact on overall demand

03:17:57.600 --> 03:17:58.770
and national income.

03:17:59.570 --> 03:18:02.550
If taxes are reduced, this, on

03:18:02.560 --> 03:18:05.050
the contrary, has a favorable effect

03:18:05.060 --> 03:18:06.950
on the growth of overall demand

03:18:06.960 --> 03:18:10.170
and national income.

03:18:13.270 --> 03:18:17.470
MPC, divided into units

03:18:17.480 --> 03:18:21.610
minus MPC, is a tax multiplier.

03:18:22.290 --> 03:18:24.910
Here it just shows how much

03:18:25.450 --> 03:18:27.650
rubles changes the total

03:18:27.660 --> 03:18:29.090
demand and national income

03:18:29.100 --> 03:18:33.370
when taxes change by 1 ruble.

03:18:33.810 --> 03:18:35.530
The tax multiplier is described

03:18:35.540 --> 03:18:37.730
in more detail in the text of

03:18:37.740 --> 03:18:38.830
the lectures.

03:18:43.220 --> 03:18:46.500
I was talking about fiscal-

03:18:46.510 --> 03:18:48.160
budgetary policies.

