03:19:12.990 --> 03:19:14.940
prices.

03:19:15.100 --> 03:19:17.560
And in order to prevent inflation,

03:19:18.020 --> 03:19:21.480
the state reduces its expenses or

03:19:21.490 --> 03:19:24.900
