03:19:36.070 --> 03:19:38.540
fact that the combined demand

03:19:38.550 --> 03:19:41.300
curve shifts to the left, and

03:19:41.310 --> 03:19:45.900
the balanced GDP returns

03:19:46.120 --> 03:19:47.820
to the potential level, look

03:19:47.830 --> 03:19:50.060
at the slide, returns to

03:19:51.480 --> 03:19:52.840
the potential level, and

03:19:52.850 --> 03:19:55.680
inflation does not occur.

03:19:59.450 --> 03:20:00.390
Well, here I would like

03:20:00.400 --> 03:20:01.710
to emphasize that all

03:20:01.720 --> 03:20:03.810
multiplicative effects at the same time

