As a result, by increasing

03:22:16.890 --> 03:22:20.280
public investment, we will get

03:22:20.290 --> 03:22:23.380
an increase in economic potential,

03:22:23.390 --> 03:22:25.980
an increase in potential GDP,

03:22:25.990 --> 03:22:29.620
