The role of the state in the transitional economy,

03:26:03.890 --> 03:26:06.080
such as the Russian economy, is important.

03:26:09.050 --> 03:26:13.590
The task of the state is to create

03:26:13.600 --> 03:26:16.110
a market infrastructure.

03:26:16.190 --> 03:26:21.690
To ensure that such structures

03:26:21.700 --> 03:26:25.050
are created that ensure the effective

03:26:25.060 --> 03:26:27.530
functioning of the market.

03:26:28.550 --> 03:26:30.510
This is a problem that no one

03:26:30.520 --> 03:26:31.830
can solve without the state.

