03:27:19.340 --> 03:27:20.560
The state's social expenditure

03:27:20.570 --> 03:27:22.260
is inefficient.

03:27:22.660 --> 03:27:26.080
The state must cease to be a

03:27:26.090 --> 03:27:29.960
cow-cow, but must create conditions

