Presidential elections were

03:38:46.990 --> 03:38:48.680
held at this time.

03:38:48.980 --> 03:38:50.420
Two candidates came together.

03:38:52.800 --> 03:38:55.760
One candidate advocated that in

03:38:56.160 --> 03:38:57.720
the field of monetary circulation

03:38:57.730 --> 03:38:59.760
everything should be left the same,

03:39:00.340 --> 03:39:02.720
that paper dollars should

03:39:02.730 --> 03:39:06.240
be bound only to gold.

03:39:06.440 --> 03:39:11.680
And his opponent was in favor

03:39:12.100 --> 03:39:13.580
of the security of paper

